PEOPLE
v.
MCCAW S236618 Supreme Court of California. AUGUST 29, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-captioned matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Second Appellate District, Division Five, with directions to vacate its decision and reconsider the cause in light of People v. Gallardo (2017) 4 Cal.5th 120 , 226 Cal.Rptr.3d 379 , 407 P.3d 55 . (See Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
